Class UniversalType

java.lang.Object
org.microbean.construct.UniversalConstruct<TypeMirror>
org.microbean.construct.type.UniversalType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Constable, AnnotatedConstruct, ArrayType, DeclaredType, ErrorType, ExecutableType, IntersectionType, NoType, NullType, PrimitiveType, ReferenceType, TypeMirror, TypeVariable, UnionType, WildcardType
public final class UniversalType extends UniversalConstruct<TypeMirror> implements ArrayType, ErrorType, ExecutableType, IntersectionType, NoType, NullType, PrimitiveType, TypeVariable, UnionType, WildcardType

      Returns a non-null, immutable List of UniversalTypes whose elements wrap the supplied List's elements.

    • of

      public static final UniversalType of(TypeMirror t, Domain domain)
      Returns a non-null UniversalType that is either the supplied TypeMirror (if it itself is null or is a UniversalType) or one that wraps it.
      Parameters:
      t - a TypeMirror; may be null in which case null will be returned
      domain - a Domain; must not be null
      Returns:
      a UniversalType, or null (if t is null)
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if domain is null
